data.SOURCE:
@AbapCatalog.viewEnhancementCategory: [#NONE]
@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Y端kleme Belgeleri'
@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
@ObjectModel.usageType:{
    serviceQuality: #X,
    sizeCategory: #S,
    dataClass: #MIXED
}
define view entity YI_NFT_DDL_IMP_SHIP_BASE 
  as select from    ynft_t_dlv_cus   as header
    inner join      ynft_t_dlvit_cus as item      on  header.companycode      = item.companycode
                                                  and header.deliverydocument = item.deliverydocument
    left outer join ynft_t_dlvit_cus as clearence on  clearence.referencedocument     = item.deliverydocument
                                                  and clearence.referencedocumentitem = item.deliverydocumentitem
{
  key header.companycode,
  key header.deliverydocument,
  key item.deliverydocumentitem,
      @Semantics.quantity.unitOfMeasure : 'quantityunit'
      item.shipquantity,
      item.quantityunit,
      clearence.deliverydocument as clearencedocument,
      header.deliverydate,
      header.loadingdate,
      header.billoflading,
      header.customsgate,
      header.customsreceivedate,
      header.invoiceno,
      header.invoicedate,
      header.fictitiousdeclerationdate,
      header.fictitiousdeclerationno,
      header.customsdeclerationdate,
      header.customsdeclerationno,
      header.importdate,
      item.incentivedocument,
      item.incentivedocumentitem,
      item.controldocument,
      item.gtipno,
      item.origin
}
where
  header.documenttype = '1'
